lines: 1. Nomwegene Yeso and' onsi as' ore?;Nar' enkoro yao kera rituko?Nor' omworokigwa? motemo' orore;Nak'Omoika, omonge kegima.
'Bogim' obonge, 'bogim' bonge;Erio babe n'obogim' obonge'Bogim' obonge, 'bogim' obonge;Erio nabe n'obogim' obonge.
2. 'S'obwanchani bwaye, orari'erieta,Ri'Omotori'omuya, orwete igoro,Bachenu sasima ase Ring'ana;Rikorw' ogotorek' as' amanyinga.
3. Inchwo mwegenete, 'gw'okorangeria;Bionsi korw' as' Are, naye moe bo,Yeso nagwanchere Korach'as'Are;Naka'ogosesenigw'okonene.
